name: hebrew
comment: This file contains lexemes/glosses from my personal collection mixed with ETCBC lexeme and glosses. When I merged the two, I linked my personal lexemes to the ETCBC lexemes, but I kept my glosses. Any new words utilize the ETCBC gloss. All lexemes use the ETCBC surface form provided by the Text-Fabric function F.voc_utf8.v(). The presence of a feature, etcbc_gloss, indicates that I have modified the term's gloss to something more preferable. The lexeme node numbers are taken from version 2017 of the ETCBC BHSA dataset.
